      <title>海外 Verizon 用户称无法连接移动网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/verizon-users-abroad-say-they-can-t-connect-to-mobile-network</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国境外漫游的威瑞森通信公司 (Verizon Communications Inc.) 移动用户报告称，从周三晚上开始，他们遇到了网络连接问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/verizon-users-abroad-say-they-can-t-connect-to-mobile-network</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称对冲基金“积极”抛售科技股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hedge-funds-are-selling-tech-stocks-aggressively-goldman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 的分析显示，在英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 短暂成为全球最大公司的一个月里，对冲基金正在“积极”抛售科技股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/hedge-funds-are-selling-tech-stocks-aggressively-goldman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:41:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国最大移动运营商 True 推出日元可持续发展贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/largest-thai-mobile-operator-true-debuts-yen-sustainability-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，泰国最大的移动电话运营商 True Corp. 正在银团发行首笔以日元计价的可持续发展相关贷款，以期在美元利率居高不下的情况下降低融资成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/largest-thai-mobile-operator-true-debuts-yen-sustainability-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及耗资 100 亿美元的风电场有望于 2026 年破土动工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/egypt-s-10-billion-wind-farm-is-poised-to-break-ground-in-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家参与建设的公司表示，世界上最大的风电场之一将于 2026 年 3 月在埃及开始建设，因为炎热夏季的严重停电凸显了这个北非国家的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/egypt-s-10-billion-wind-farm-is-poised-to-break-ground-in-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国能源亿万富翁加大数据中心建设力度，抢占人工智能热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thai-energy-billionaire-steps-up-data-center-push-to-tap-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国第二大富豪、能源亿万富翁萨拉特·拉塔纳瓦迪 (Sarath Ratanavadi) 正在加速进军数据中心领域，以挖掘云计算和人工智能需求不断增长所推动的蓬勃发展的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thai-energy-billionaire-steps-up-data-center-push-to-tap-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CVC 同意收购英国基础设施承包商 M Group Services</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/cvc-agrees-to-buy-uk-infrastructure-contractor-m-group-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CVC Capital Partners Plc 已同意收购英国基础设施承包商 M Group Services，这是该私募股权巨头的又一笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/cvc-agrees-to-buy-uk-infrastructure-contractor-m-group-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中资荷兰芯片制造商将在德国投资 2 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/chinese-owned-dutch-chipmaker-to-invest-200-million-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上海上市公司闻泰科技股份有限公司旗下的荷兰芯片制造商 Nexperia Holding BV 将投资 2 亿美元在其汉堡生产工厂开发和生产半导体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/chinese-owned-dutch-chipmaker-to-invest-200-million-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银将以 30 亿美元投资人工智能初创公司 Perplexity</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团旗下的愿景基金 2 号正在以 30 亿美元的估值投资美国人工智能初创公司 Perplexity AI，这是孙正义对该领域的最新押注，他认为该领域对于确保自己的遗产至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/softbank-to-invest-in-perplexity-in-ai-race-against-google-rivals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光股价因预测未达到预期而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机内存芯片制造商美光科技公司 (Micron Technology Inc.) 早盘股价下跌，原因是其预测令寻求从人工智能狂热中获得更多回报的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/micron-falls-after-forecast-fails-to-meet-lofty-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国数据遭黑客入侵，包括新生儿和癌症患者数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/stolen-data-across-uk-signals-hospital-hack-worse-than-disclosed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦医院攻击事件背后的黑客最近公布了包括英国和爱尔兰境内孕妇、新生儿、癌症患者、精神分裂症患者及数千名其他人的个人信息的记录，这表明此次攻击的规模远比当局此前指出的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/stolen-data-across-uk-signals-hospital-hack-worse-than-disclosed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
